! 1.2 Operable Windows (use SimpleOpening to allow for both infiltration & ventilation)

! C = ELA_i * √(2 * rho_air * ∆P_ref) / (Perimeter_i * ∆P_ref^n)
! C = 0.00017610 kg/s-m (Air mass flow coefficient when opening is closed)

